<@U3063KMGT> 

```
Bundle bundle = new Bundle();
bundle.putParcelable("myAwesomeParcelable", Parcels.wrap(myAwesomeObject));
```
wrap your object and convert it to Parcelable
yes, I tried with Otto its working to pass from activity to multiple fragments but not to multiple activities.

And to get it back in other activity

```
Parcels.unwrap(getIntent().getParcelableExtra("myAwesomeParcelable"));
````
Try parceler! The library I shared above
it eliminates the boilerplate
